BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260306T063600
DTEND:20260306T100600
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.733ft at 06:36\n-2.959ft at 10:06\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Holding shorter-period NW swell\, along with a secondary pulse of S Southe
 rn Hemi\, will keep surf in the waist to shoulder high zone for good spots
  in the morning. Mid day high tide will slow tide sensitive breaks. Waves 
 dip a bit in the afternoon as the swell starts to ease. \n\nLight northerl
 y wind expected in the morning\, staying light while getting more variable
  in the afternoon. Conditions in town due to stay clean to semi clean all 
 day. 
END:VEVENT
