SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260307T063600
DTEND:20260307T113600
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.766ft at 06:36\n-2.982ft at 11:36\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Fading mix of short-period NW swell and smaller S Southern Hemi pulse is s
 till good for thigh to stomach high waves in the morning\, then surf taper
 s off during the day. Mid day high tide slows down tide sensitive breaks. 
 \n\nLight winds\, mainly northerly\, and favorable conditions in town due 
 all day. 
END:VEVENT
